* [sol1-C]

```C
bool isValid(char * s) {
    int len = strlen(s);
    int top = 0;
    char stack[len];
    for (int i = 0; i < len; i++) {
        char c = s[i];
        stack[top++] = c;
        if (top >= 3 && strncmp(stack + top - 3, "abc", 3) == 0) {
            top -= 3;
        }
    }
    return top == 0;
}
```

